window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Here starts an adventure that will span lifetimes and worlds. Discover where the story begins.</p> <p>Raymond E. Feist is an internationally best-selling author.</p> <p>My name is Pug. I was once an orphaned kitchen boy, with no family and no prospects, but I am destined to become a master magician…</p> <p>War is coming to the Kingdom of the Isles from another world, bringing with it chaos and destruction. Pug yearns to train as a warrior and fight for his kingdom alongside his foster-brother, Tomas, but instead he is forced to follow a different path: a path that will lead him right into the heart of the enemy. And one that will change the course of the war – and two worlds – forever.</p> <p>So begins the most epic series in fantasy fiction, a tale that will cross worlds and generations.</p> <p>Magician is the first book in the Riftwar Saga. The trilogy continues with book two, Silverthorn.</p>"; 
